# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# starwarsffg — .gitignore
#
# NOTE: This is a Foundry VTT *system*. Everything Foundry loads at runtime
# ships in the repo, so the following are DELIBERATELY tracked (do not ignore):
#   - lib/        vendored libs referenced by system.json (slimselect,
#                 datatables, jszip, jxon, pure, @swrpg-online). This includes
#                 their dist/, *.min.js, and *.map files — hence NO global
#                 dist/ or *.map ignores below.
#   - images/, fonts/   shipped assets
#   - styles/*.css      compiled CSS is checked in (no SCSS build in this tree)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Node / tooling (appears after `npm install` of devDependencies)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm/
.eslintcache

# Backups & scratch files
*.bak
*.orig
*.tmp
*~
# ...but keep this one: it's a documented rollback reference for the DataModel
# migration (see modules/datamodels/README.md — the revert procedure restores
# it over template.json).
!template.full.json.bak

# OS cruft
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor / IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.code-workspace
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# Local env / secrets (in case any tooling ever needs them)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Foundry may symlink/copy this system into its data dir; ignore any nested
# Foundry userdata that could accidentally land here.
Data/
Logs/
Config/
